01:31.591 --> 01:37.597 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They promise to positively and
meaningfully
impact the lives of the men and
women we represent.

01:37.630 --> 01:39.399 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

01:39.432 --> 01:41.935 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority
Leader: And,
at the end of the day, this is
an agreement

01:41.968 --> 01:49.542 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
that reflects our basic
principles, something
both Democrats and Republicans
can support.

01:49.576 --> 01:53.279 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: President Trump
told Bloomberg
News he's -- quote -- "very
happy" with the

01:53.313 --> 01:54.280 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
bill.

01:54.314 --> 01:55.281 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
What's in it?

01:55.315 --> 01:57.617 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
First, what was a sticking
point, security.

01:57.650 --> 02:02.322 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
