President Trump
priority, the border wall.

02:17.036 --> 02:21.574 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Despite that loss, Vice
President Mike Pence,
speaking on CBS, called the deal
a bipartisan

02:21.608 --> 02:23.443 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
win.

02:23.476 --> 02:25.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE PENCE, Vice President of
the United States:
It'll avert a government
shutdown, but more

02:25.245 --> 02:29.616 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
