hollowed out in
recent years by budget cuts.

02:34.020 --> 02:38.591 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Outside of
defense, and in
contrast to President Trump's
proposals, few

02:38.625 --> 02:40.760 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
