broad priorities,
what they did here.

04:19.459 --> 04:20.793 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Republicans made one big
trade-off.

04:20.827 --> 04:22.895 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
