about do not
yet have majority of approval in
polling,

05:24.090 --> 05:25.692 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
like Planned Parenthood.

05:25.725 --> 05:28.194 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
