continue to be
funded.

05:28.227 --> 05:32.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So if they are willing to shut
down government
over something that is
unpopular, they think

05:32.098 --> 05:33.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that will go blow up against
them.

05:33.366 --> 05:35.735 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So they didn't take those
stances in this
bill.

05:35.768 --> 05:39.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: You touched on
some of the
very broad things that were
being cut or being

05:39.138 --> 05:40.907 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
supported.

05:40.940 --> 05:44.577 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
But there are some very
specific, real people
that are targeted here or
benefit here.

05:44.610 --> 05:45.578 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Tell us about those people.

05:45.611 --> 05:46.679 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: I get to use
more graphics.

05:46.713 --> 05:47.680 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
