Palm Beach,
they have a lot of residents in
common, I

06:07.300 --> 06:09.168 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
think often, in winner and
summer.

06:09.202 --> 06:11.571 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
