and down
the East Coast in particular,
Amtrak is getting

06:28.888 --> 06:30.423 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a big funding boost.

06:30.456 --> 06:32.658 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Now, not everyone did all that
well.

06:32.692 --> 06:37.430 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A couple of things that I
noticed that did
get some cuts, you might not
hear about, the

06:37.463 --> 06:39.232 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Coast Guard.

06:39.265 --> 06:42.068 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
