observer, this
certainly seemed like a
relatively civil process,

07:00.920 --> 07:05.358 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with not the usual sort of
fighting and recriminations.

07:05.391 --> 07:08.461 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
