this, or do you
think this actually could be a
change in the

07:08.494 --> 07:09.462 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
tone on Capitol Hill?

07:09.495 --> 07:10.430 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Imagine that.

07:10.463 --> 07:12.198 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I don't think so, actually.

07:12.231 --> 07:15.601 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
