07:54.774 --> 07:57.376 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think, we look ahead, a lot of
these things,
they are going to kick down the
can.

07:57.410 --> 08:00.880 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I also understand that the White
House has
been saying tonight that they
will bring the

08:00.913 --> 08:03.649 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
