this summer.

08:03.683 --> 08:07.887 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I think we're going to be
regurgitating
all of these issues again.

08:07.920 --> 08:09.689 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Republicans will have more and
more chances
to get their votes.

08:09.722 --> 08:11.390 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We will see if they do.

