29:35.373 --> 29:40.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hill -- our Politics Monday duo
breaks it
all down; and a
behind-the-scenes look at

29:40.912 --> 29:44.282 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one of the world's fastest
