Welcome to you both.

35:39.937 --> 35:41.139 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Good
to be here.

35:41.172 --> 35:42.006 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Amy, I would
