victory?

36:38.629 --> 36:41.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: Yes,
and if you liked this movie,
just wait.

36:41.632 --> 36:42.667 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
