37:42.293 --> 37:43.027 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Right, no car
crashes, no
Vin Diesel.

37:43.060 --> 37:44.829 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: No Vin Diesel.

37:44.862 --> 37:47.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Was this just
a case where
the GOP was scared that they
were going to

37:47.698 --> 37:49.533 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
