37:49.567 --> 37:53.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Yes, if you control
the government,
you get all the blame, and you
get the credit.

37:53.471 --> 37:59.744 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the bottom line is, we have
seen now in
these past 100 days that,
despite the fact

37:59.777 --> 38:04.081 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
